WEBVTT

00:02.560 --> 00:03.280
Prince of Ning

00:03.800 --> 00:04.960
The family head has a message

00:05.200 --> 00:06.640
Chancellor Chen's meaning is

00:16.280 --> 00:17.640
The family head's meaning is

00:18.120 --> 00:18.760
In matters

00:19.200 --> 00:20.160
Either don't do it

00:20.520 --> 00:21.040
Or

00:21.280 --> 00:22.480
Do it completely

00:22.680 --> 00:23.760
His meaning is

00:28.600 --> 00:29.920
Let me think about it

00:30.320 --> 00:30.920
Your Highness

00:31.040 --> 00:31.800
Delay will cause trouble

00:31.800 --> 00:32.160
Your Highness

00:32.160 --> 00:33.000
How dare you

00:34.400 --> 00:35.200
Since when

00:35.200 --> 00:37.040
Has Chancellor Chen been making decisions for me?

00:37.080 --> 00:37.600
I wouldn't dare

00:38.040 --> 00:39.000
This subordinate was presumptuous

00:39.120 --> 00:39.800
Didn't understand clearly

00:40.160 --> 00:41.080
Spoke wrongly

00:48.160 --> 00:48.840
Second son

00:49.200 --> 00:50.640
Our father didn't have you publicly tried

00:50.640 --> 00:52.040
But had me interrogate you

00:52.400 --> 00:53.440
What does that mean?

00:53.960 --> 00:55.480
You should understand in your heart

00:56.120 --> 00:57.680
Since Chu Huan is willing to step forward

00:58.120 --> 00:59.600
I can use him to fulfill my duty

01:10.400 --> 01:11.000
Second brother

01:11.400 --> 01:12.760
As long as you admit to poor management

01:12.760 --> 01:13.840
And negligence that harmed the state

01:14.160 --> 01:15.320
You can leave here

01:15.760 --> 01:17.720
And live freely as a prince

01:19.080 --> 01:20.040
As for Chu Huan

01:20.840 --> 01:22.560
I can delay his execution

01:23.600 --> 01:25.040
When I become emperor in the future

01:25.160 --> 01:26.120
I'll ensure he doesn't die

01:26.800 --> 01:27.520
What do you say?

01:33.640 --> 01:34.560
Second brother

01:35.160 --> 01:36.640
Think of your princess

01:37.080 --> 01:38.400
Can you bear to let her follow you

01:38.400 --> 01:39.560
And ruin her life like this?

01:44.600 --> 01:45.280
Second son

01:45.840 --> 01:47.400
If you let go now

01:48.160 --> 01:49.600
We can still be brothers
